# Add these environment variables to your environment (e.g. to Netlify, or a .env file)
CONTENTFUL_SPACE_ID=[copy your Space ID from the Contentful dashboard]
CONTENTFUL_ACCESS_TOKEN=[copy your API token, either the live or preview one. Generally it's the preview one you want for local development.]
CONTENTFUL_HOST=[priview.contentful.com for previews, cdn.contentful.com for live data]
GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_CREDENTIALS=[Create a Service Account for your Google API Project that has access to Google Sheets, minify it, and encode in base64.]